EZ Moves® Furniture Moving System allows you to easily slide furniture into place across any surface. Includes an EZ Moves® furniture lifter and eight slides for both carpet and hard sufaces.
Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.

transcripts: Moving furniture is a real struggle, no matter how hard you try you need more than one guy. Hi I'm David Jones here to show you how you can move any piece of furniture in your home by yourself. This is e.z. moves. The do it yourself furniture moving system. Now that's easy. Just lift, place, and slide. The e.z moves furniture lifter gives you up to 10 times your natural strength. Then the e.z moves slide right into place so that your furniture simply glides across any surface and then slide right out when you're done. Get your easy moves furniture system today.
